The Functionality for my Leaderboard:

Add Summoner
    Add summoner to track matches
Get Summoner Info
    Fetch Riot profile, rank, etc.
Get Match History
    Get latest matches (N=10/20)
Label Match
    Add a tag/label to a match
Get Leaderboard
    Compare tracked players

